OL,3,CShop price inflation edges up as
OL,4,C'storm clouds loom' ` BRC
OL,6,FShop price inflation edged up in March
OL,7,Fas higher costs resulting from the
OL,8,FMiddle East conflict started to feed
OL,9,Finto supply chains, figures show.
OL,11,FShop prices overall were 1.2% higher
OL,12,Fthan a year ago, up from 1.1% in
OL,13,FFebruary but still below the three-
OL,14,Fmonth average of 1.3%, according to
OL,15,Fdata from the British Retail
OL,16,FConsortium (BRC) and NIQ.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
