CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774933457
OL,3,CShop price inflation edges up as
OL,4,C'storm clouds loom' ` BRC
OL,6,FThe BRC warned that "storm clouds
OL,7,Floom" despite "subdued" inflation and
OL,8,Fnoted the headline figure rose even as
OL,9,Ffood inflation eased from 3.5% to 3.4%
OL,10,Fdue to dairy prices falling with lower
OL,11,Fwholesale milk costs.
OL,13,FInflation on non-food items rose to
OL,14,F0.1% against a drop of 0.1% in
OL,15,FFebruary despite retailers offering
OL,16,Fpromotions on alcohol, TVs and sound
OL,17,Fsystems in the run-up to the final
OL,18,Fround of the Six Nations, as well as
OL,19,Fon clothing and footwear to entice
OL,20,Fconsumers to spend.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@EO]oD@OOUoD@WO]
