FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774933457
OL,3,CShop price inflation edges up as
OL,4,C'storm clouds loom' ` BRC
OL,6,FMike Watkins, head of retailer and
OL,7,Fbusiness insight at NIQ, said: "Whilst
OL,8,Fit's good news that food inflation
OL,9,Fslowed in recent weeks, shoppers are
OL,10,Fincreasingly conscious of the amount
OL,11,Fof money they are spending at the
OL,12,Fcheckout and non-food retailers will
OL,13,Fbe hoping for a good Easter to drive
OL,14,Fsales.
OL,16,F"However, if price rises come through
OL,17,Fthe supply chain over the next few
OL,18,Fmonths, this has the potential to take
OL,19,Fthe edge off retail growth."
OL,26,@oD@`OUxD@AOU{D@\O]
